{"id":584106,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/05/【立此存照】新浪微博敏感词：包子-零阅读/","date":"2018-05-05T10:46:42Z","modified":"2018-05-05T10:46:42Z","title":"【立此存照】新浪微博敏感词：“包子” = 零阅读","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>2018年5月5日，微博用户 <a href=\"https://weibo.com/u/1759932171\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@yangxinshu</a> 发现自己发布的一条批评中式父权的内容的阅读数为零，同时有网友表示自己无法转发该条微博，<strong>这意味着新浪对其做了屏蔽处理</strong>。作者原本以为敏感的是批评父权的内容，结果经过多次测试后发现，在保持其他内容不变的情况下，<strong>删去某句中的“包子”二字，这则内容就能正常发表和转发。</strong></p>\n<p>显然，新浪微博地对“包子”一词采取了不易让人察觉的、更隐蔽的审查方式。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584111\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584111\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词4.jpg 1214w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词4-300x185.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词4-768x474.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词4-1024x633.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词4-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>被悄悄审查的“零阅读”微博内容：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词1-copy.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584107\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词1-copy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"375\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词1-copy.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词1-copy-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词1-copy-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 375px) 100vw, 375px\" /></a></p>\n<p>原作者删除“零阅读”微博中的“包子”二字即后可正常发布：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584108\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584108\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"424\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词3.jpg 1222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词3-300x243.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词3-768x621.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词3-1024x828.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">删除“包子”后顺利发出的微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p>有微博用户表示自己虽然能看到，但却无法转发原作者的微博内容：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_584109\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0076d7NMgy1fr0klex0gcj30cp06sjry.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584109\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0076d7NMgy1fr0klex0gcj30cp06sjry.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"214\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0076d7NMgy1fr0klex0gcj30cp06sjry.jpg 457w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/0076d7NMgy1fr0klex0gcj30cp06sjry-300x160.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">图片来源：新浪微博 @-妖_妖-</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_584110\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-584110\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"143\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词2.jpg 1216w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词2-300x82.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词2-768x210.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/05/包子敏感词2-1024x280.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,16848,27949],"tags":[25995,8859,8616]}